message.body: Yo man, you got anything going on tomorrow night?
Yeah. I can't go out or nothing til like may 17. Why what's goin on?
Oh shit. Why not? You doing a study? Just trying have to a few peeps come out in phoenixville then do after party at my place with the fire pit...
Haha why are you fb messaging me as we'll?
I fb messaged u before u texted me. Just say in hi lol yeah gotta study. Mad intense. $3500 tho
Damnnnnn. What does it involve?
Taken drugs/givin blood. U know how I do
And no drinking apparently?
Nope
Booooo
Gotta get paid yo. Big plans this summa
Oh yeah? Like what?
Bout to get this beach house for fourth of July week. Goto Cali. Pay off some debt goto a few shows. Get some new npire equipment
Weren't you talking about going to Vegas?
Yeah that was eds thing but that's a no go now
Haha understandable...
That woulda been phat tho. One day one day...so I see u got Ur phone back after it was stolen?

No never got it back... :( I was able to track it down to a specific street in north wales but the GPS is only accurate within 100ft so we weren't able to determine which house out of the row homes my phone was in so I had to buy a new one
Oh dam. All that for nothing eh. Def got got
For sure.
Did keV make a movie about it? lol
No. He was legit googling every house though and finding out who lives there and their phone numbers then calling them and asking if they had any information. Hagan
Haha* neighbors we quick to rat out the kids that live around them
Damn . What street was it. North Wales is my old stomping grounds
It was back in some housing development..
Rutledge ct... I think it was off of horsham rd
Haha I dun understand stealing phones. It can't work for them right?

For some you can but I don't think for mine they would be able to. I had an app on my phone called find my iPhone and once I got home I was able to put a lock on my phone and make it so they could only see the message I displayed for them...
Oh damn. Sounds like quite the ordeal. U goin to Liz's benefit?
Uhm. I'm not sure, when is it?
June 1 6pm
I'm not sure, I'd have to figure it out closer to the date
Word
